original_title: Star Trek: The Next Generation - A XXX Parody
overview: Lt. Commander Data finds Tasha Yar alive on a barren planet near the Romulan Neutral Zone. She appears to be the Tasha who went down with the Enterprise C and ended up on Romulus. Slowly she adjusts to her familiar, yet different crew.
